                </item>
                <item style="text-decoration: none;border-style: none;user-select: none;-webkit-user-select: none;-ms-user-select: none;outline-style: none;color:inherit;/*! background: white; */margin-bottom:10px;padding: 20px;/*! border-radius:10px; */text-align: left;height: auto;width: auto;/*! box-shadow: 0 3px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.12),0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.24); */display: flex;flex-direction: column;">
                    <span style="text-decoration: none;border-style: none;user-select: none;-webkit-user-select: none;-ms-user-select: none;outline-style: none;font-size: 22px;font-weight: bold;margin-bottom:5px;text-transform: uppercase;border-bottom: 5px solid #9932CC;background: #E1B4F7;padding-left: 5px;color: #9932CC;">Our History</span><span
                            style="text-decoration: none;border-style: none;user-select: none;-webkit-user-select: none;-ms-user-select: none;outline-style: none;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;line-height: 1.5;margin-top: 5px;text-align: justify;">Mishusoft Systems Incorporated is a software development company that is going to be established with a view to offering quality IT solutions at home and abroad. The company is keen to take the advantage of fast growing global software and data processing industry by offering professional service and price for support and benefit of the valued customers.</span><span
                            style="text-decoration: none;border-style: none;user-select: none;-webkit-user-select: none;-ms-user-select: none;outline-style: none;font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;line-height: 1.6;margin-top: 5px;text-align: justify;">Mishusoft Systems Incorporated has started its journey to provide quality output and they are well linked internationally. Mishusoft Systems Incorporated has unique and holistic approaches toward continuous improvement through training and development of human resources to adapt into the market aiming to meet the demands of client and keep them constant touch with the latest global technological development. Mishusoft Systems Incorporated. IT is striving to provide a cost effective and high standard services in the dynamic IT industry. The company would build itself with a strategy of continuous reeducation and motivation to create an innovative and dedicated work force in the expanding IT sector.</span><span
                            style="text-decoration: none;border-style: none;user-select: none;-webkit-user-select: none;-ms-user-select: none;outline-style: none;font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;line-height: 1.6;margin-top: 5px;text-align: justify;">Mishusoft Systems Incorporated especially aims at export oriented software development. Thus Mishusoft Systems Incorporated it industry is growing at a higher rate and opening opportunities of service linkage to professional service providers all over the world.</span>
